metadata.name: RHDC YR01 1
metadata.description: RHDC YR01 is our first collection on the Road to Total Domination of an IRL sport! Our objective is to create a blueprint for Sportfans to take back control of sports! We're going lay the foundations for fans all over the world to own,manage and prosper from the teams they support! Join us on this journey as we build our very own horse racing and breeding empire! We will combine the blockchain and bloodstock worlds into one!
